*"On laže iz dana u dan." (He is lying day after day.) 

*"Ne bih rekla da laže, ali njegove izjave nisu istinite." (I wouldn't say he is lying, but his statements are not true.) 

*"Niko ne voli ljude koji lažu." (No one likes people who lie.) 

*"Oni koji lažu nikada ne bi trebalo da dobiju veru." (Those who lie should never be given trust.) 

*"Lagati je najgora stvar koju možeš da uradiš." (Lying is the worst thing you could do.) 

*"Lažući sebi, on je postao svoj najveći neprijatelj." (By lying to himself, he became his own worst enemy.)